Hey. you good?

517
00:39:40.812 --> 00:39:42.474
Yeah. about 40
miles outside of town.

518
00:39:42.647 --> 00:39:45.776
As far as I can tell.
it's isolated in Superior.

519
00:39:46.217 --> 00:39:47.845
<i>Well. that's something.</i>

520
00:39:48.086 --> 00:39:49.145
What about you? You okay?

521
00:39:50.788 --> 00:39:52.552
What did you expect?

522
00:39:53.791 --> 00:39:55.316
Like it or not. I'm
gonna find a cure.

523
00:39:56.427 --> 00:39:58.225
Yeah. I know you are.

524
00:39:59.130 --> 00:40:01.861
Man. things are
screwy right now.

525
00:40:02.066 --> 00:40:05.195
And I know we don't have any answers.
but at least we got one win. you know?

526
00:40:05.837 --> 00:40:07.396
Yeah. I hear you.

527
00:40:07.805 --> 00:40:09.450
<i>All right. I'm gonna run
Jenna up to her grandmother's.</i>

528
00:40:09.474 --> 00:40:10.874
<i>shouldn't be more
than a few hours.</i>

529
00:40:11.009 --> 00:40:12.500
Then we clean up that town.

530
00:40:12.677 --> 00:40:14.669
We find The Darkness
and we kick her ass.

531
00:40:15.013 --> 00:40:17.505
Yeah. that's great.
Dean. That. um...

532
00:40:18.016 --> 00:40:19.143
Sounds like a plan.

533
00:40:26.124 --> 00:40:29.686
If you're as bad as they say
you are. why haven't you hurt me?

534
00:40:29.928 --> 00:40:32.830
For the same reason
that you'll never hurt me.

535
00:40:38.336 --> 00:40:40.271
We're bound. Dean.

536
00:40:41.839 --> 00:40:43.705
We'll always be bound.

537
00:40:45.610 --> 00:40:47.101
You helped me.

538
00:40:47.812 --> 00:40:49.246
I helped you.

539
00:40:49.981 --> 00:40:51.779
No matter where I am.

540
00:40:52.884 --> 00:40:54.216
who I am.

541
00:40:55.053 --> 00:40:57.352
we will always help each other.

542
00:42:24.409 --> 00:42:25.409
English -SDH
